category: X11
requires: cygwin libgltext0.3.1
external-source: gltext
sdesc: "OpenGL truetype font renderer (development)"
ldesc: "GLText is a portable font rendering library for C++ OpenGL
applications. It uses FreeType2 to read and render high-quality TrueType fonts
with a minimal footprint. With just a few easy lines of C++, you can add
gorgeously rendered text to your graphical applications."
